# cntrl_alt_lenny's three-agent decomp framework — brain/decomper/scaffolder
# Claude Code sessions (see github.com/cntrl-alt-lenny/decomp-agent-framework).
# Framework files (.claude/, AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, docs/briefs/, docs/state.md,
# docs/decomp-workflow.md, docs/research/) are tracked in this fork so a fresh
# `git clone` on any machine works out of the box.
#
# To submit upstream PRs (cntrl-alt-lenny:<branch> → xbret:main) without
# carrying the framework files, branch off `upstream/main` instead of
# `origin/main`:
#   git fetch upstream
#   git checkout -b fix-foo upstream/main
#   # work, push, open PR on GitHub
# Set up the upstream remote once per clone:
#   git remote add upstream https://github.com/xbret/xenoblade.git
